data.description:
Discover your dream home at 16 Tallyho Turn, nestled in the serene Equestrian Run cul-de-sac. This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom property boasts a master suite with an attached office, two additional upstairs bedrooms, and a convenient downstairs bedroom. The home features a spacious dining room, enhanced with numerous upgrades.

Key highlights:

Fully Furnished option available
Brand new exterior paint and siding (2023)
Modern laminate waterproof flooring downstairs (2023)
Fresh carpet upstairs (2022)
Elegant granite countertops (2022)
New stainless steel appliances (2022; Dishwasher installation upcoming)
Updated HVAC system (2022)
Contemporary garage door (2022)
Recently installed water heater (2022)
Newly built patio (2023)
Custom lighting in dining room and kitchen (2023)
Garage with painted walls and epoxy floor
Enjoy proximity to Langley AFB, I-64, and shopping centers. Note: No listing agent solicitations, please.
